Master KG thanked everyone who made Jerusalema a world-wide hit. It currently has more than 220 million views on YouTube. Master KG had been nominated for the MTV award alongside his fellow countryman DJ Maphorisa, Nigeria's Burna Boy and Uganda's Sheebah among others. Burna Boy won the 2019 award with previous recent winners being Nigeria's Wizkid (2016), Davido (2017) and Tiwa Savage (2018). --BBC--